	Enjoy your favourite incense sticks and cones in true style with this delightful carved incense burning smoke box. Simply light the tip of your incense stick, blow the flame out and place in the specially designed hole or place a cone in one of the two specially designed wells then sit back and enjoy indulgent relaxation with a beautiful aroma. With the option of burning two incense sticks or incense cones at the same time, you can combine your favourite fragrances to create your own unique aroma. You can even close the lid and allow the smoke to evenly drift through the intricate lattice design and gently fill your home with gorgeous scents. This incense holder is ideal for keeping your furniture safe from any unwanted burn marks or messy falling ash. This black coloured wooden smoke box is decorated with a stars and moon pattern. It is an ideal incense burner and makes a beautiful gift when accompanied by incense. Box dimensions: 305mm long x 57mm wide x 64mm tall.</p>
